 to know > Search results for 'Kate Bush' (from irishcharts.ie)|publisher=Imgur.com (original source published by Fireball Media)|accessdate=2019-07-28}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.2em;font-size:90%;\"| [[MegaCharts|NLD]]<br /><ref name=\"dutchcharts\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.2em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br /><ref name=billboard200/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''4 Sucessos''<br/>{{small|(two-part release)}}{{cn|date = October 2019}}\n|\n*Released: 1978\n*Label: [[EMI Records|EMI]] {{small|(Brazil)}}\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[On Stage (EP)|On Stage]]''\n|\n*Released: 31 August 1979\n*Label: EMI\n| 10\n| 15\n| 17\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Kate Bush (EP)|Kate Bush]]''\n|\n*Released: 15 June 1983\n*Label: EMI\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 148\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Aspects of the Sensual World]]''\n|\n*Released: 1990\n*Label: Columbia {{small|(US)}} / [[Capitol Records|Capitol]] {{small|(Canada)}}\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Eat the Music]]''\n|\n*Released: 1993\n*Label: Columbia {{small|(US)}}\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n|colspan=\"6\" style=\"font-size:90%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|-\n|}\n\n== Singles ==\n{{See also|List of songs recorded by Kate Bush}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\" border=\"1\"\n|+ List of singles, with selected chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"11\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br /><ref name=occ/><ref name=UKmix>UK singles chart peaks for \"There Goes a Tenner\" and \"Lyra\": {{cite web|url=https://i.imgur.com/G29Jpul.jpg|title=UK Mix forums > Chart Histories page 78|publisher=ukmix.org|