| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| ''The Red Shoes''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[King of the Mountain (song)|King of the Mountain]]\"\n| 2005\n| 4\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 5\n| \u2014\n| 42\n| 13\n| 13\n| \u2014\n| 47\n| \u2014\n| ''Aerial''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Lyra (song)|Lyra]]\"\n| 2007\n| 187\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| ''[[The Golden Compass_(film)#Music|The Golden Compass]]'' soundtrack\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Deeper Understanding]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2011\n| 87\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 92\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| ''Director's Cut''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Wild Man (Kate Bush song)|Wild Man]]\"\n| 73\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| ''50 Words for Snow''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Running Up That Hill#2012 remix|Running Up That Hill]]\" {{small|(2012 Remix)}}\n| 2012\n| 6\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 22\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| ''[[A Symphony of British Music (album)|A Symphony of British Music]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"And Dream of Sheep\" {{small|(live)}}\n| 2016\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| ''Before the Dawn''\n|-\n|colspan=\"14\" style=\"font-size:90%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart or was not released in that territory.\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Promotional singles ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\" border=\"1\"\n|+ List of singles\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Moving (Kate Bush song)|Moving]]\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1978\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''The Kick Inside''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Them Heavy People]]\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Room for the Life\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"